    },
    {
      "id": "section-1",
      "title": "Base Design's Strategic Brand Overhaul",
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "id": "para-1-0",
          "content": "Base Design collaborated with The Huntington through on-site interviews and focus groups to develop the brand identity, strategy, naming, and signage.Key team members included Min Lew, Mirek Nisenbaum, Geoff Cook, Jeffrey Waldman, Carlos Bocai, Darius Wang, Harry Laverty, Romain Bourillon, Katerina Mery, Shirlin Kao, and Alyssa Bishop.The new monogram balances institutional gravity with contemporary confidence, avoiding California clichés while clarifying the institution's \"360° nature where nature and knowledge meet.\"",
          "citations": [
            {
              "primarySource": {
                "id": "source-7",
                "name": "huntington",
                "url": "https://www.huntington.org/news/huntington-launches-multiyear-initiative-land",
                "favicon": "https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=www.huntington.org&sz=32",
                "title": "The Huntington by Base Design"
              },
              "additionalCount": 1,
              "additionalSources": [
                {
                  "id": "source-3",
                  "name": "huntington",
                  "url": "https://www.huntington.org/news/huntington-announces-ambitious-2026-exhibition-and-installation-schedule",
                  "favicon": "https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=www.huntington.org&sz=32",
                  "title": "The Huntington by Base Design"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "para-1-1",
          "content": "President Karen R. Lawrence described the rebrand as supporting priorities like connecting collections and expanding access digitally and in person.The design provides \"clearer tools to articulate what it has always been,\" without changing the mission or programs.It scales effectively for digital platforms, addressing limitations of the prior ornate mark.",
          "citations": [
            {
              "primarySource": {
                "id": "source-6",
                "name": "southpasadenan",
                "url": "https://southpasadenan.com/the-huntington-launches-bold-rebrand-and-digital-initiatives-to-enhance-visitor-experience/",
                "favicon": "https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=southpasadenan.com&sz=32",
                "title": "The Huntington by Base Design"
              },
              "additionalCount": 1,
              "additionalSources": [
                {
                  "id": "source-8",
